{"tid":438020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日聽人講嘢超過三分鐘就已經專注唔到","createTime":"2017-10-16T13:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T14:44:48.000Z","uid":64838,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d39fd8d706c50ced048a046f02c7dc2f9f954a91","tid":438020,"uid":64838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論係平時上堂,開會,定係同人傾計都好<br />\n一過左三分鐘就不知不覺咁分左神諗其他野<br />\n一分左神三十秒再專注返就發覺已經甩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其是依家part time讀書,平時放完工就番學/做功課,根本無咩時間去預習,成日去上堂一走左神就成堂唔知發生緊咩事,上堂好似淨係抄notes咁完全跟唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有改善方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679516ac99e8721ecb02d4a1df257ac8cfa533d6","tid":438020,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"係咪唔夠訓"},{"pid":"4e55cf76143c02ede88cd01537f4b5e189e4216c","tid":438020,"uid":64838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪唔夠訓</blockquote><br />\n應該唔係,有時好精神都會自己唔覺咁走左神去諗其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b8992b0b9c52b45fd2c1e7ffeaa01a3b78e916","tid":438020,"uid":61766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"Me too 有時聽個上司教野 聽聽下自己都唔知自己個心飛左去邊"},{"pid":"0695e0e44fa7072b6f0e8cd49f767e9f8e57abff","tid":438020,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"專注力不足？ 可以睇下醫生"},{"pid":"22fe38bb59e8aeb5e47b26